<view class="home-container">
  <view class="search-section">
    <view class="search-card">
      <view class="search-title">搜索酒店</view>
      <view class="search-subtitle">输入酒店名称关键词，快速查找想住的酒店</view>
      <view class="search-row">
        <view class="search-field">
          <van-search
            value="{{ searchValue }}"
            shape="round"
            background="transparent"
            placeholder="请输入酒店名称"
            bind:change="onSearchChange"
            bind:search="onSearch"
          />
        </view>
        <van-button type="info" round custom-class="search-btn" bindtap="onSearch">
          搜索
        </van-button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="quick-section">
    <view class="section-title">快捷入口</view>
    <view class="quick-card" bindtap="navigateTo" data-url="/pages/hotel/hotel">
      <view class="quick-icon">
        <van-icon name="wap-home-o" size="36rpx" color="#1989fa" />
      </view>
      <view class="quick-content">
        <view class="quick-name">浏览全部酒店</view>
        <view class="quick-desc">查看酒店列表、进入详情页并开始预订</view>
      </view>
      <view class="quick-arrow">
        <van-icon name="arrow" size="28rpx" color="#c8c9cc" />
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="quick-tip">“我的订单”和“个人中心”已保留在底部导航栏，首页不再重复展示。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="banner-box">
    <image class="banner-img" src="../../assets/logo.jpg" mode="aspectFill"></image>
    <view class="banner-text">从首页搜索酒店后，可继续查看详情、选择房型、填写入住信息并完成下单支付。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="service-fab" bindtap="goToCustomerService">
    <view class="service-fab-icon">
      <van-icon name="service-o" size="36rpx" color="#ffffff" />
    </view>
    <view class="service-fab-text">
      <view class="service-fab-title">智能客服</view>
      <view class="service-fab-subtitle">快速咨询</view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>